The Year of the Dragon update has a vibrant new theme bursting with fireworks, lanterns, Chinese knots, and red envelopes. Plus, the Mighty Eagle gets a special Year of the Dragon makeover! 

Puzzle your way through 15 new Chinese New Year levels!
Enjoy special seasonal surprises!
Use Fireworks to blast through difficult levels!

